# ============================================================================
# .gitignore - Minimal Configuration to Upload All Project Files
# ============================================================================
# This is a minimal .gitignore that allows all project files to be uploaded
# Only system-specific files are excluded

# ============================================================================
# OS SPECIFIC FILES ONLY
# ============================================================================
# macOS
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
._*

# Windows
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# ============================================================================
# IDE CACHE (Optional - Remove if you want to include IDE settings)
# ============================================================================
# Visual Studio Code cache
.vscode/.history

# ============================================================================
# END OF .gitignore
# ============================================================================
# All other files including:
# - Source code (.cpp, .hpp, .h)
# - Executables (.exe)
# - Libraries (SFML/)
# - Resource files (.ttf, .wav)
# - Build output (output/)
# - Documentation (README.md)
# Will be uploaded to GitHub

